#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Cstandards-compliance.md:7
msgid "**BIO** (Baseline Informatiebeveiliging Overheid)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Cstandards-compliance.md:7
msgid ""
"Overall information security baseline. RONL implements BIO controls "
"including access management (Keycloak RBAC), audit logging (PostgreSQL), and "
"secure transmission (TLS everywhere)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Cstandards-compliance.md:7
msgid "**NEN 7510**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Cstandards-compliance.md:7
msgid ""
"Information security in healthcare settings. Applied to the handling of "
"citizen health-related data (zorgtoeslag eligibility)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Cstandards-compliance.md:7
msgid "**AVG / GDPR**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Cstandards-compliance.md:7
msgid ""
"Data minimisation (BSN encrypted, not logged in plaintext), audit trail (7-"
"year retention), purpose limitation (process variables scoped to the "
"requesting service)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Cstandards-compliance.md:7
msgid "**DigiD Norm**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Cstandards-compliance.md:7
msgid ""
"Authentication assurance levels (LoA) for citizen-facing services. RONL "
"enforces LoA checks on sensitive endpoints via the `loa` JWT claim."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Cstandards-compliance.md:7
msgid "**NCSC Beveiligingsrichtlijnen**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Cstandards-compliance.md:7
msgid ""
"Secure software development practices, dependency management, vulnerability "
"disclosure."
msgstr ""

